<div class=3DWordSection1>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Mining valuable resou=
rces
from planets, moons, asteroids and gas clouds across the galaxy is an impor=
tant
part of your empire&#8217;s economy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Types of Mining<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>There are three types=
 of
mining:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l=
0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
