</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Gas mining</span></b><span style=3D'mso-no-proof=
:yes'>:
extracting gas resources, e.g. fuel sources like Caslon or Hydrogen, or oth=
er
gases used in manufacturing various components<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-fa=
mily:
Symbol;mso-no-proof:yes'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<span
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Standard mining</span></b><span style=3D'mso-no-=
proof:
yes'>: extracting all other types of strategic resources, e.g. metals,
gemstones, polymer, silicon, etc<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0=
 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-fa=
mily:
Symbol;mso-no-proof:yes'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<span
