&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Luxury resource mining</span></b><span
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>: extracting luxury resources that are used to i=
mprove
colonies<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Mining Locations<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

